Welcome to the Trading Platform project! This platform is designed for educational purposes to explore and track stock market data using real-time APIs.


Features
Search Stocks: Enter a stock symbol to get current and historical prices.
View Chart: Visualize stock price trends with interactive charts.
Educational Disclaimer: Prices and data displayed may not be accurate or up-to-date.
Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Charting Library: Chart.js
API: Polygon API for fetching stock data
Setup Instructions
To set up this project locally, follow these steps:

Clone this repository: git clone https://github.com/your-username/trading-platform.git
Navigate to the project directory: cd trading-platform
Open index.html in your web browser.
Make sure to replace the API with your own as this was just for learning purposes

Credits
Chart.js: Open source charting library for JavaScript.
Polygon API: Provides real-time and historical stock market data.
